{"tid":1280150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：惡意製造對立對抗　只會斷送香港前途","createTime":"2019-07-03T01:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T01:32:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a773050f50ba266c0293b0e5519d9bf8659367","tid":1280150,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:13:01.000Z","msg":"中國人民日報發表文章，認為發生在香港的極端暴力行為，遭到各界強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n無底線的自由，絕不是幸事；不講法治的民主，只能帶來禍亂。香港雖有不錯的家底，但經不起折騰，經不起內耗，惡意製造對立對抗，只會斷送香港前途。法治是香港的核心價值，嚴懲違法行為，是對法治最好的維護，認為太平山下應享太平。<br />\n<br />\n另外，人民日報海外版的文章認為，暴力禍港者必須嚴懲，指極端激進分子以反對特區政府有關條例修訂為藉口，製造暴力事件，踐踏香港法治，破壞香港社會秩序，損害香港的根本利益，是對「一國兩制」底線的公然挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，極端激進分子利用相關事件進行暴力對抗，意圖早已不再是修例事件本身，而是旨在破壞「一國兩制」和衝擊香港特區政府管治，想通過把香港搞亂火中取栗，實現一小撮人的政治野心。"},{"pid":"ea569f4a48fbf5c0d012e25537bcee6564683f19","tid":1280150,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:13:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466361-20190703.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466361-20190703.htm&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsIVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=bf941c32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466361-20190703.htm&h=1f47e1c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466361-20190703.htm</a>"},{"pid":"021731bf194158200b8af919402c01219a4d3911","tid":1280150,"uid":131696,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"抗爭的話 香港前途或者只有黑白<br />\n但不抗爭的話 香港前途只有黑色"},{"pid":"d4b323384bcceaf4968396161ca3b5daea46da55","tid":1280150,"uid":54921,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:15:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人民日報反對的，我支持<br />\n人民日報支持的，我反對</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dcc326945c900bcdf7867d7bf7545a87ae0406cf","tid":1280150,"uid":64337,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:16:32.000Z","msg":"22年前零2日已經被斷送"},{"pid":"22ab424316a523ad82073df712378b36efd7fff8","tid":1280150,"uid":81154,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"賊喊捉賊，制造對立咪當權者囉。"},{"pid":"62bd1d27e1c631dd0298988c6733b3ef10bf35b0","tid":1280150,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"支那狗唔應該有自由，所以留係支那打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca7628207d07b6040a0bc9d721c22611cf73111","tid":1280150,"uid":8441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"想通過把香港搞亂火中取栗，實現一小撮人的政治野心<br />\n<br />\n中共捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28705561be2ddf2807e0d2f687031a47f71a419c","tid":1280150,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:18:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8127f716e68ebe220e94facb72d3375541fcfe9a","tid":1280150,"uid":237284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:19:27.000Z","msg":"當權者有重視民意<br />\n有真正落區視察民生<br />\n唔奶共賣港<br />\n邊有人得閒同你政治野心<br />\n用命同你暴力呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕裂果位係暴政</span></span>"},{"pid":"69b3527202ec0fa27565ea97881b39b099893bbd","tid":1280150,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:20:48.000Z","msg":"中國唔搶走香港打壓咪冇對立囉"},{"pid":"cf8491b716923bc2f7e571175efea1eb47ab422f","tid":1280150,"uid":49669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:21:42.000Z","msg":"冇錯，香港政府製造社會矛盾，與市民對抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0015b2e8c786fb13085e0adf6bf585ebf7bdcf","tid":1280150,"uid":245033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":